dc_description_s: This data represents public lands for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'County_Lands', 'Federal_Lands', and 'State_Land'.County Lands: [The County Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent County Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]State Land: [The State Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent State Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]Federal Lands: [The Federal Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent Federal Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
